data.description: This home is completely move in ready and gives you so much house for the money, so stop your scroll...sprawling ranch with 3 bedroom, 2 baths, large kitchen with separate dining room, large living room, 3 car garage and large yard! New flooring throughout, as well as paint, light fixtures, and fridge. Primary en suite has tiled bath, large walk in closet and is very spacious. Yard fully fenced with deck and 1 car garage attached and 2 car detached with rear alley access and architectural shingle roof 2020. Homes roof 2009, deep crawl space, Anderson windows, radon mitigation system. Existing Home Warranty through January 2025.
